description: This Right Angle Converter can convert a 7.4mm (Outside diameter) x 5.08mm (Inside diameter) straight power connector on some Dell and HP/Compaq laptop computer power adapters to a right angle connector.Note: This LC90 connectorwill notwork for some Dell power adapters that have octagon shape connectors. It only works forround shape7.4mmx 5.08mm connectors with center pin, such asDell Inspiron Series: 300m, 500m, 510m, 600m, 630m, 640m, 700m, 710m, 13, 1318, 15, 14z, 1420, 1470, 15z, 1501, 1520, 1521, 1525, 1526, 1545, 1570, 6000, E1405, E1505, 1150, 1320, 14, 1410, 1425, 1427, 1440, 17, 1720, 1721, 1750, 6400, 8500, 8600, 9200, 9300, 9400, E1705Dell Lititude D Series LaptopsDell Studio, Dell Vostro Series LaptopsHP / Compaq Laptop Computers:This converter is only for  HP Compaq laptops that using a big  power connector with center pin. The outside diameter of the connector is 7.4mm.  It will not work for  HP Compaq power  connector without center pin.This adapter may work for:Compaq CQ 20, CQ35, CQ40, CQ50, CQ60 SeriesCompaq V3700, V3800, V3900, V6500, V6600HP G seriesHP Pavilion dm1, dm2, dm3, dm4, dm5, dm6, dm7, dv3 dv4, dv5, dv6, dv7 seriesPartial HP Pavilion  dv9600, dv9700, dv9800, dv9900 series that  with big 7.4mm  connector with center pin.Does not work for HP Compaq power adapters that have  no center pin.HP Compaq business notebook series such as  2210b, 2510p, 2710p,  6510b, 6515b, 6710b, 6710s, 6715b, 6715s, 6720S,  6820S, 6910p,  8510p, 8710p and other models that  with big 7.4mm outside diameter round power connector.
title: BiXPower LC90B Right Angle 90-degree 7.4 X 5.0mm Connector Converter for Dell and Hp / Compaq Laptop Power Adapters
